 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Mar 20, 2010 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
“Speak out for those who cannot speak, for the rights of all the destitute.” (NRSV)
</p>

 <p>
According to  <i>Sojourners</i>, 25% of U.S. adults polled attributed this quote to either Obama or the Dalai Lama. (February 2010, p. 9)
